### Login and save Token automatically
POST http://localhost:8080/psacms/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "officer_001@example.com",
  "password": "secure_password"
}

> {%
    // Save the raw token returned by the server into a global variable.
    client.global.set("auth_token", response.body);
  %}
